  "text": "where s = |\u2207n|/n 4/3 is the reduced density gradient. \u03b5 sr,PBE c,md (n, s, \u03b6, \u00b5) interpolates between the usual PBE correlation functional, 43 \u03b5 PBE c (n, s, \u03b6), at \u00b5 = 0 and the exact large-\u00b5 behavior, [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] 44 yieldin\u1e21",
